# Phase 1: Assessment and Planning (Q2 2025)

## Objective
Assess the current state of PaySafe Retailâ€™s systems and plan for PCI-DSS v4.0 compliance.

## Tasks
- Conduct a gap analysis to compare current security controls against PCI-DSS v4.0 requirements.
- Identify in-scope systems, including code repositories and CI/CD pipelines impacting the Cardholder Data Environment (CDE).
- Assign a project lead to manage the transition.
- Develop a detailed project timeline and resource allocation plan.
- Document roles and responsibilities for compliance tasks.

## Timeline
- Start: April 2025
- End: June 2025

## Deliverables
- Gap analysis report
- Project timeline
- Roles and responsibilities document
